Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.84,0:00:04.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Wednesday Downtown,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.35,0:00:09.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let’s get on with our first presenter please
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:16.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's Jinnai Tomonori!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.96,0:00:19.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:24.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, this time I've brought an annual project
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.39,0:00:28.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The 8th Best Lyrics Adaptation Championship
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:30.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here we go
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it the 8th edition already?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:34.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's the 8th year, the 8th edition
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:38.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is much more anticipated than other competitions
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:40.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In the 6th and 7th, Hollywood Zakoshi dominated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.92,0:00:42.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.37,0:00:45.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's obviously good, but I don't remember it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:46.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed \N -Only remember watching it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:48.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But this time the judges have also changed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:51.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The jury for the 8th edition is senior citizens
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.96,0:00:54.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The age has gone up again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.43,0:00:57.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seniors over 75 years old are the judges
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:00:58.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.40,0:01:01.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is this so Hollywood Zakoshi doesn't win again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:04.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If its the same as before he'll just win again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:05.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How dare you admit it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.80,0:01:09.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, he is still able to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.41,0:01:12.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just like Ernesto Hoost  \N-Indeed, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.88,0:01:14.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The Annual Competition
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.32,0:01:16.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Celebrating its 8th edition this year
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:19.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The Best Adaptation Lyrics Tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.33,0:01:23.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tonight, a new group of eight singing comedians assemble
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:29.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time the judges are senior citizens
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.30,0:01:30.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Senior citizens?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:37.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I feel like older people will laugh if they're encouraged to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:39.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,More-so than young people
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.08,0:01:43.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The elderly may laugh at those who sing well
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:48.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They definitely prefer people who can sing well, so I'm really in the running
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.32,0:01:51.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I have a very powerful secret strategy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:57.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you curry favor with them, it's possible to win by a large margin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:01:57.99,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:02:02.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They are my most important target audience
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:08.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I originally became a comedian in order to make older people laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:08.51,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Already bullshit.\N  -Already lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:10.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Right in the center of the bullseye
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:15.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I often consider whether I can capture the hearts of that age group of viewers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.25,0:02:18.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I also adapt lyrics to sing to senior citizens
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:20.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For example, Hibari Misora
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:27.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Ahhhhh, the flow of water, help me"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.59,0:02:28.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It can be triggered at once
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:34.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I actually did not want to become a parody artist
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:37.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Actually, I wanted to be a lyric rewriter
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:40.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So I'm planning to debut today
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.71,0:02:44.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hey, how come no one has been able to defeat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:46.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You guys, come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:48.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Gos Gos Gos Gos
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:50.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.25,0:02:52.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The above 8 are the participants
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:57.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,From the first round to the final round, they will adapt the lyrics of three designated songs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:00.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The judges are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:04.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,51 seniors aged 75 or older
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The oldest age is 88 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:11.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who will be able to capture the hearts of the older people to win the title?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:13.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:21.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan's new serialization project begins after a 3 year absence
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:24.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fs75}I don't understand, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:25.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fs75}This Wednesday, right?
