Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:44.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I heard myself in his songs and it felt interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:48.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The 2nd one i'm a bit unsure what he was singing about
