Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.39,0:42:11.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.24,0:42:15.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What'd be the point if they all like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.85,0:42:24.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, as some girls have been included to pretend to like him
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.79,0:42:36.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can Kuro-chan find a girl who really likes him and get a girlfriend after 10 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.07,0:42:40.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is the purpose of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.54,0:42:46.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, what about the 2 people eliminated today?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.31,0:42:49.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Which side are those 2 people on?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.15,0:42:53.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They were both pretending
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.98,0:42:56.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No way, absolutely no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.95,0:42:59.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It can't be true, seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.82,0:43:02.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's awful
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.03,0:43:04.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was lying, sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.43,0:43:09.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Pretending to like Kuro-chan is a bit too tiring
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.33,0:43:12.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To be honest there is nothing that I like about him
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.48,0:43:13.83,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Understandable
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.10,0:43:14.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?  \N-Really
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.60,0:43:17.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.07,0:43:19.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Women are scary
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.28,0:43:19.40,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He was fooled
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.40,0:43:25.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I felt so guilty after eliminating them because I really thought they liked me
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.82,0:43:27.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So that means you can't tell
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.25,0:43:30.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.49,0:43:36.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If those 2 people are fake...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.13,0:43:37.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It feels like everyone is fake now
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.08,0:43:41.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.00,0:43:44.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this line?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.49,0:43:50.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now, the remaining members will start living with Kuro-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.01,0:43:53.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The setting is once again Okinawa
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.38,0:43:56.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.69,0:43:59.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I am trying to get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.92,0:44:01.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm not playing around
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.80,0:44:02.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can I kiss you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.69,0:44:04.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I hope you only like me
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.62,0:44:08.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}I like you the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.24,0:44:09.55,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.89,0:44:14.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}I don't trust the girl who likes me
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.19,0:44:20.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.37,0:44:24.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's up with this secrecy?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.64,0:44:27.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is not a simple love project at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.72,0:44:32.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's for sure.\N  -Not everyone wants to make good memories with that lowly man
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.08,0:44:35.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We don't know how many are sincere \N  -Correct
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.62,0:44:39.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are a few people who are lying, but we don't know who  \N-Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.02,0:44:43.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But 3rd place Risa is lying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.39,0:44:45.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Risa?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.44,0:44:48.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After all, its impossible to believe that Kuro-chan's mouth doesn't stink
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.96,0:44:51.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who knows? I've never smelled it either
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.37,0:44:53.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It stinks
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.51,0:44:54.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It definitely stinks, doesn't it? \N -It stinks
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.69,0:44:56.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You haven't smelled it either
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.67,0:44:57.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It just stinks
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.94,0:44:59.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It can't stink 24 hours a day
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.68,0:45:03.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't know why i'm sticking up for Kuro-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.55,0:45:10.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are they crying because they're happy or because they want out? \N -Yes, yes, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.76,0:45:13.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It could be either
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.95,0:45:16.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's unclear what the tears are expressing
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.29,0:45:19.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's acting, maybe it's true
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.70,0:45:20.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's scary
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.80,0:45:24.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Michopa you can't stand him, but you're also curious, right?  \N -No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.10,0:45:26.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To see what'll happen
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.04,0:45:28.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't care about his love life at all
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.04,0:45:32.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I just want him to be cheated
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.30,0:45:36.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan looks happy right now
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.20,0:45:37.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But also a little suspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.61,0:45:41.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I hope the program team quickly torture him to death
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.33,0:45:42.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's too much!
